antlr.preprocess

Class FunctionBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • antlr.preprocess.FunctionBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FunctionListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class FunctionBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements FunctionListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of FunctionListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
